<plot>Norma Shaw, a sweet, little old Grandmother is PETA person of the year for her work with endangered ducks. However, when Norma discovers that a cardinal is pecking at her bedroom window; morning, noon and night... it's war! Norma tests her beliefs and values trying everything she can think of to free herself of the tenacious, little red bird.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?094211</url></doc>
